Author: phmwls
Text: Sometimes I also think it’s a lot of food they’re eating but I don’t think it’s what they actually eat every single day. Also, it’s a huge responsibility to post that online bc you never know if someone impressionable is watching so I’m sure they at least try to make it healthier than it actually is by either adding food groups or amounts of food, yknow?
